1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:25,789 --> 00:01:30,030
[My Heart]

3
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:32,800
[Episode 7]

4
00:01:33,780 --> 00:01:36,700
So... So you mean

5
00:01:37,180 --> 00:01:38,180
I ate too much, huh?

6
00:01:39,460 --> 00:01:40,820
I don't mind how much you ate.

7
00:01:40,820 --> 00:01:42,050
You can eat as much as you can.

8
00:01:42,259 --> 00:01:43,460
But you need to pay the bill!

9
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:46,620
Gosh!

10
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:47,979
I remember Baihe told me that

11
00:01:48,020 --> 00:01:49,180
the residents in No Magic Valley

12
00:01:49,580 --> 00:01:50,940
buy things with silver.

13
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:57,540
Excuse me,

14
00:01:58,140 --> 00:02:00,740
I-I came to this place for the first time,

15
00:02:01,980 --> 00:02:02,730
so I have no money.

16
00:02:04,139 --> 00:02:05,539
I have seen so many people like you!

17
00:02:05,979 --> 00:02:06,860
You have no money, huh?

18
00:02:06,860 --> 00:02:07,340
OK!

19
00:02:07,740 --> 00:02:09,740
Stay here and wash dishes to pay for your debt.

20
00:02:09,900 --> 00:02:10,410
I...

21
00:02:10,700 --> 00:02:11,820
Actually, I have money

22
00:02:12,780 --> 00:02:14,220
but I don't take any.

23
00:02:14,620 --> 00:02:15,740
If you let me go home,

24
00:02:15,780 --> 00:02:17,620
I'll come back with money right away, okay?

25
00:02:17,620 --> 00:02:18,380
No way!

26
00:02:19,260 --> 00:02:19,820
Waiter,

27
00:02:20,980 --> 00:02:22,220
how much is it? I'll pay her bill.

28
00:02:22,460 --> 00:02:23,530
All these dishes!

29
00:02:29,329 --> 00:02:30,780
Is this enough for the dishes?

30
00:02:32,620 --> 00:02:33,460
Yes. Yes. Yes.

31
00:02:33,980 --> 00:02:35,540
You can order some more dishes if you want.

32
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:36,820
Do you want more?

33
00:02:37,940 --> 00:02:39,260
N-no, I don't.

34
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:43,540
Welcome to come again!

35
00:02:53,780 --> 00:02:55,820
Are you following me?

36
00:02:56,100 --> 00:02:57,260
You think too much.

37
00:02:57,660 --> 00:02:59,500
I heard a disturbance from far away,

38
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:01,660
so I went to have a look. As expected, it's you.

39
00:03:02,610 --> 00:03:04,700
I don't have money here.

40
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:06,820
Wait.

41
00:03:08,140 --> 00:03:08,940
What do you mean?

42
00:03:10,860 --> 00:03:12,900
Look, we are closely connected these days,

43
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:15,980
which indicates that our relationship
is hard to cut off.

44
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:19,100
As the old saying goes, "People decreed
by destiny will meet from far away,

45
00:03:19,420 --> 00:03:21,060
while others can't meet
even though they are close."

46
00:03:22,579 --> 00:03:24,579
Since we are connected by destiny,

47
00:03:24,890 --> 00:03:26,100
we'd better not cut the rope off

48
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:27,180
and be tied to the same rope.

49
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:28,820
What the hell are you talking about?

50
00:03:28,940 --> 00:03:30,140
I read it in a novel.

51
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:34,050
I'm not familiar with this place.

52
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:36,740
What if I get bullied by bad people?

53
00:03:37,980 --> 00:03:38,820
Listen to me.

54
00:03:39,060 --> 00:03:40,300
I wouldn't look for you if you get lost.

55
00:03:43,220 --> 00:03:44,060
I'm in a good mood today.

56
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:45,340
You can buy anything you like.

57
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:46,500
Really?

58
00:03:46,500 --> 00:03:47,060
Yeah.

59
00:03:52,329 --> 00:03:53,020
Look at this.

60
00:04:05,060 --> 00:04:05,540
Listen.

61
00:04:05,740 --> 00:04:07,060
Have you heard the sound of the sea crying?

62
00:04:07,250 --> 00:04:07,940
I can't hear anything.

63
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:08,980
You can!

64
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:12,660
Bakery!

65
00:04:13,130 --> 00:04:14,700
Osmanthus cake is my favorite dessert.

66
00:04:14,890 --> 00:04:15,700
Buy me some, please!

67
00:04:15,899 --> 00:04:17,660
You've just eaten a whole table of dishes!

68
00:04:18,170 --> 00:04:19,500
But, dishes are dishes

69
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:20,540
and dessert is dessert.

70
00:04:20,540 --> 00:04:21,580
How could they be the same?

71
00:04:23,260 --> 00:04:23,780
Excuse me.

72
00:04:23,850 --> 00:04:26,900
Ice-sugar gourd! Sweet and sour!

73
00:04:28,260 --> 00:04:29,300
Ice-sugar gourd!

74
00:04:29,460 --> 00:04:30,820
Come on, choose by yourself.

75
00:04:32,860 --> 00:04:34,260
Can you eat two by yourself?

76
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:36,020
This is for you.

77
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:53,620
Is this where you live in No Magic Valley?

78
00:04:54,580 --> 00:04:55,580
It's much better than Lord Jin Mansion...

79
00:04:55,940 --> 00:04:56,820
Stop. Stop.

80
00:04:58,620 --> 00:04:59,860
It's late now,

81
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:00,980
so you can sleep here tonight.

82
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:01,500
But

83
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:02,820
I should make it clear that

84
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:03,700
you can only stay here for three days,

85
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:04,820
and then you need to go back home.

86
00:05:05,020 --> 00:05:06,460
I don't want to be involved
in your runaway event.

87
00:05:06,860 --> 00:05:07,540
Three days?

88
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:11,300
That's too short.

89
00:05:12,660 --> 00:05:13,220
Ten days!

90
00:05:13,340 --> 00:05:13,930
Ten?

91
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:15,100
No. Just three days.

92
00:05:15,180 --> 00:05:16,340
No! Then seven days!

93
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:17,500
No. Only three days.

94
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:18,820
No! Then five days!

95
00:05:18,820 --> 00:05:19,700
Five days, deal!

96
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:22,180
You're tricking me!

97
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:25,060
Here in my place,

98
00:05:25,060 --> 00:05:26,420
you can't live and eat for free.

99
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:30,420
But I have neither magic power

100
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:32,300
nor silver.

101
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:34,700
What about this?

102
00:05:34,780 --> 00:05:35,540
You can take the place of Xiaowu

103
00:05:35,580 --> 00:05:37,700
to take care of me these days, okay?

104
00:05:48,420 --> 00:05:49,300
I'm so tired.

105
00:05:49,300 --> 00:05:50,180
You can live here.

106
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:51,540
But I must tell you first,

107
00:05:51,580 --> 00:05:53,180
that you need to remember
a few rules for living here.

108
00:05:54,100 --> 00:05:55,050
Rules?

109
00:05:55,050 --> 00:05:56,540
You are my servant girl now.

110
00:05:56,540 --> 00:05:57,340
How dare you protest me!

111
00:05:58,220 --> 00:06:00,370
OK, fine.

112
00:06:00,580 --> 00:06:01,100
First,

113
00:06:01,210 --> 00:06:02,500
keep the room clean and neat.

114
00:06:02,860 --> 00:06:03,450
Second,

115
00:06:03,450 --> 00:06:04,660
keep the bed clean and neat.

116
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:05,540
Third,

117
00:06:05,580 --> 00:06:06,740
keep yourself clean and neat.

118
00:06:06,740 --> 00:06:07,180
Do you remember?

119
00:06:09,100 --> 00:06:09,970
Y-yes.

120
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:11,580
Have a good rest.

121
00:06:23,060 --> 00:06:24,220
I do remember the rules,

122
00:06:25,180 --> 00:06:26,620
but I can't promise to follow them.

123
00:06:29,260 --> 00:06:31,540
Let me think about what to eat for dinner.

124
00:06:43,340 --> 00:06:45,420
Why does the fire go up and down randomly?

125
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:46,940
It has a bad temper!

126
00:06:47,580 --> 00:06:49,860
On Qiyuan continent,
we make fire with magic power.

127
00:06:50,460 --> 00:06:52,180
I didn't know it's that hard!

128
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:22,420
Are you okay?

129
00:07:22,730 --> 00:07:23,500
I'm fine.

130
00:07:23,930 --> 00:07:24,820
Look at the dishes I made.

131
00:07:25,300 --> 00:07:26,340
Although they don't look good,

132
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:27,780
they should taste good.

133
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:29,500
You cooked only one dish
and got yourself so dirty.

134
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:31,500
You may destroy the kitchen if you cook more!

135
00:07:31,659 --> 00:07:32,060
That's enough.

136
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:33,220
You can go and have a rest.

137
00:07:59,340 --> 00:08:00,970
Lord Jin not only boasts great magic power,

138
00:08:01,660 --> 00:08:02,980
he can also cook well.

139
00:08:03,460 --> 00:08:04,660
He is awesome!

140
00:08:09,420 --> 00:08:10,140
Can I start eating?

141
00:08:10,140 --> 00:08:10,820
Just eat. Eat it.

142
00:08:13,860 --> 00:08:14,820
Eat slowly.

143
00:08:14,940 --> 00:08:16,020
Nobody would grab your food.

144
00:08:21,770 --> 00:08:22,820
This is delicious!

145
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:24,180
Especially this soup!

146
00:08:24,780 --> 00:08:25,660
What's it?

147
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:26,580
Cattail soup.

148
00:08:26,580 --> 00:08:27,020
What?

149
00:08:27,450 --> 00:08:29,130
So this is cattail soup.

150
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:31,059
I learned to cook the soup

151
00:08:31,220 --> 00:08:32,460
from one of my old friends.

152
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:33,980
He used to cook this for his wife.

153
00:08:34,659 --> 00:08:36,690
His wife must be very happy!

154
00:08:38,780 --> 00:08:39,660
But unfortunately,

155
00:08:39,860 --> 00:08:41,050
his wife passed away later,

156
00:08:41,700 --> 00:08:43,210
so he makes the soup very often.

157
00:08:43,780 --> 00:08:45,100
Each time he drinks the soup,

158
00:08:45,180 --> 00:08:46,540
it reminds him of his wife.

159
00:08:46,540 --> 00:08:49,020
He also names it "cattail soup".

160
00:08:49,780 --> 00:08:51,340
Cattail soup...

161
00:08:52,140 --> 00:08:53,620
Cattail is as resilient as silk

162
00:08:53,740 --> 00:08:54,860
and rock is tough and won't change.

163
00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:56,180
You know this poetry.

164
00:08:56,380 --> 00:08:57,180
Amazing.

165
00:08:57,620 --> 00:08:59,300
The man is like a rock

166
00:08:59,300 --> 00:09:00,620
and his wife is like a cattail.

167
00:09:01,700 --> 00:09:03,140
I was not allowed to go out of home
since my childhood,

168
00:09:03,460 --> 00:09:04,700
so I read lots of novels

169
00:09:05,100 --> 00:09:06,300
and heard many stories.

170
00:09:06,690 --> 00:09:07,740
I knew this line at that time,

171
00:09:08,140 --> 00:09:09,660
and I was deeply moved!

172
00:09:10,980 --> 00:09:14,380
Although people in No Magic Valley
have no magic power,

173
00:09:14,980 --> 00:09:17,500
they have real love and affection.

174
00:09:18,260 --> 00:09:19,420
Human beings

175
00:09:19,420 --> 00:09:20,820
shouldn't have been

176
00:09:20,820 --> 00:09:21,860
classified by magic power.

177
00:09:24,300 --> 00:09:24,860
Yeah.

178
00:09:25,380 --> 00:09:26,300
There should be no distinction

179
00:09:27,460 --> 00:09:29,100
among all of us.

180
00:09:31,820 --> 00:09:32,370
Let's eat.

181
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:39,100
Your Highness.

182
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:41,900
Do you know where Qingqing is?

183
00:09:42,100 --> 00:09:42,740
Not yet.

184
00:09:42,740 --> 00:09:44,260
I'll give you reinforcements.
Go and find her as soon as possible.

185
00:09:44,420 --> 00:09:44,820
Yes, Your Highness.

186
00:09:57,380 --> 00:09:57,900
Your Highness,

187
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:58,900
Lady Yunxi has arrived.

188
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:00,420
Have you found Qingqing?

189
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:03,140
Your Highness,

190
00:10:03,580 --> 00:10:04,980
Qingqing fled without permission

191
00:10:05,220 --> 00:10:06,570
and has brought you a lot of trouble,

192
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:08,180
I should apologize for her.

193
00:10:10,180 --> 00:10:11,340
I made some dessert.

194
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:13,780
Would you like yo sit down and have a try?

195
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:16,980
Qingqing is lively and active.

196
00:10:17,740 --> 00:10:19,460
She must have learned
too many rules all at once,

197
00:10:19,900 --> 00:10:20,650
so she had to run away

198
00:10:21,260 --> 00:10:23,260
under a lot of pressure.

199
00:10:23,540 --> 00:10:24,100
Your Highness,

200
00:10:24,460 --> 00:10:25,780
please don't worry about her too much.

201
00:10:26,330 --> 00:10:28,220
Father's already got extra men looking for her,

202
00:10:28,460 --> 00:10:30,660
so I believe she'd come back soon.

203
00:10:30,820 --> 00:10:31,700
She has no magic power.

204
00:10:32,460 --> 00:10:34,900
I don't know how much danger she'll encounter.

205
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:42,060
My sister fled without permission.

206
00:10:42,540 --> 00:10:45,060
Aren't you mad at her?

207
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:48,980
I'm just mad at

208
00:10:49,860 --> 00:10:51,820
myself for failing to recognize
her anxiety in time.

209
00:10:53,050 --> 00:10:54,140
If I noticed it earlier,

210
00:10:55,330 --> 00:10:57,420
she wouldn't have been so depressed.

211
00:11:02,220 --> 00:11:03,860
[Thin Strip of Sky]

212
00:11:03,860 --> 00:11:06,760
[Lilu Villa]

213
00:11:23,690 --> 00:11:24,530
Why did you come in?

214
00:11:25,860 --> 00:11:26,380
Isn't...

215
00:11:26,700 --> 00:11:28,660
Isn't this my bedroom?

216
00:11:28,820 --> 00:11:29,900
Your bedroom is on the other side!

217
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:32,180
Sorry.

218
00:11:32,180 --> 00:11:33,610
I have a poor sense of direction.

219
00:11:38,500 --> 00:11:39,220
Hold on.

220
00:11:51,540 --> 00:11:52,460
Take it!

221
00:11:54,340 --> 00:11:54,900
Thank you.

222
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:11,180
What? What happened?

223
00:12:12,860 --> 00:12:13,860
What's that?

224
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:16,580
What do you mean?

225
00:12:16,780 --> 00:12:18,540
I just saw a black

226
00:12:18,540 --> 00:12:20,140
and fluffy little monster went past.

227
00:12:20,900 --> 00:12:22,100
Just a mouse.

228
00:12:24,180 --> 00:12:24,980
Did it leave?

229
00:12:25,100 --> 00:12:25,980
It's already...

230
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:44,380
Have a good rest

231
00:12:44,660 --> 00:12:45,740
and be careful not to catch a cold.

232
00:12:46,220 --> 00:12:47,570
Are you caring about me?

233
00:12:49,100 --> 00:12:50,220
I don't want to be infected.

234
00:12:51,460 --> 00:12:51,980
Well,

235
00:12:52,580 --> 00:12:54,660
can you go get me a cup of water?

236
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:26,490
[Lilu Villa]

237
00:13:25,780 --> 00:13:26,140
Nangong!

238
00:13:31,060 --> 00:13:33,300
You are coming at the right time!

239
00:13:33,980 --> 00:13:34,540
Are you

240
00:13:35,140 --> 00:13:36,660
in a relationship?

241
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:44,900
Don't talk nonsense!

242
00:13:45,220 --> 00:13:46,300
You've thought too much!

243
00:13:46,580 --> 00:13:47,660
We slept in two different bedrooms.

244
00:13:49,460 --> 00:13:52,380
So, you two live together

245
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:53,900
in the same house.

246
00:13:54,020 --> 00:13:54,780
What are you thinking?

247
00:13:54,900 --> 00:13:55,380
Eat the meal,

248
00:13:55,580 --> 00:13:56,740
and then I'll take you to Commander's House.

249
00:13:56,940 --> 00:13:57,660
OK. OK.

250
00:13:58,770 --> 00:13:59,540
Commander's House?

251
00:14:00,860 --> 00:14:01,660
What's that place?

252
00:14:02,620 --> 00:14:03,180
It's my home.

253
00:14:03,260 --> 00:14:04,220
I also want to go there.

254
00:14:04,460 --> 00:14:05,100
No...

255
00:14:05,180 --> 00:14:06,300
You'd better stay here.

256
00:14:06,970 --> 00:14:08,900
It's so boring if I stay here alone.

257
00:14:09,090 --> 00:14:09,660
Besides,

258
00:14:09,660 --> 00:14:10,740
the reason why I left Qiyuan continent

259
00:14:10,740 --> 00:14:12,220
was to see the world.

260
00:14:12,740 --> 00:14:13,660
Just take me with you!

261
00:14:14,060 --> 00:14:15,540
I could carry your bag or something, you know.

262
00:14:17,260 --> 00:14:18,540
Qingqing is so cute.

263
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:20,540
If you don't take her,

264
00:14:21,300 --> 00:14:22,620
I will.

265
00:14:23,700 --> 00:14:24,980
She is my servant girl now.

266
00:14:25,100 --> 00:14:26,900
I'm the only one who can take her, right?

267
00:14:28,650 --> 00:14:31,460
[Commander's House]

268
00:14:31,460 --> 00:14:32,510
[Hande Dwelling]

269
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:33,460
The Commander's House is so splendid!

270
00:14:33,900 --> 00:14:34,660
Lord Jin,

271
00:14:46,940 --> 00:14:48,300
can I play it?

272
00:14:48,980 --> 00:14:50,380
Sure. Go play it for a while.

273
00:14:52,220 --> 00:14:52,900
Don't get hurt.

274
00:14:53,660 --> 00:14:54,740
Be careful! Don't hurt yourself!

275
00:14:55,060 --> 00:14:56,020
I see!

276
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:05,340
Father.

277
00:15:07,620 --> 00:15:08,330
Nangong is coming.

278
00:15:09,540 --> 00:15:10,180
Great Commander,

279
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:11,140
long time no see.

280
00:15:11,620 --> 00:15:12,060
Lord Jin.

281
00:15:12,940 --> 00:15:13,540
As you were.

282
00:15:14,540 --> 00:15:15,890
You seldom come to my home.

283
00:15:16,660 --> 00:15:17,820
What's the matter?

284
00:15:18,220 --> 00:15:19,740
Recently, the magic power army
camouflage themselves

285
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:21,940
and search for the magic girl's whereabouts
in our valley.

286
00:15:22,140 --> 00:15:23,020
This way is wicked

287
00:15:23,140 --> 00:15:25,540
and has broken the peace treaty
between the two places.

288
00:15:25,770 --> 00:15:28,290
I wonder what you think of this.

289
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:30,500
To tell you the truth,

290
00:15:31,450 --> 00:15:33,180
I also came here today for an important matter.

291
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:34,300
I want to ask for your instructions.

292
00:15:36,060 --> 00:15:36,580
Please.

293
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:37,060
Please.

294
00:15:41,740 --> 00:15:43,010
Great Commander, please have a look.

295
00:15:46,010 --> 00:15:49,120
[Imperial Edict
I'll pass the throne to my son, Nangong Yixin.]

296
00:15:48,380 --> 00:15:48,980
This is

297
00:15:50,100 --> 00:15:51,500
an edict from the late Emperor Nangong?

298
00:15:52,820 --> 00:15:53,290
Exactly.

299
00:15:54,180 --> 00:15:54,860
As you can see,

300
00:15:55,180 --> 00:15:57,380
my father wanted me to ascend the throne.

301
00:15:57,980 --> 00:15:59,260
But you know my personality.

302
00:15:59,660 --> 00:16:01,490
I have no interest in the throne at all.

303
00:16:01,660 --> 00:16:02,860
I don't want to fight with Mingyang,

304
00:16:03,980 --> 00:16:04,980
but the traitor ministers in court

305
00:16:04,980 --> 00:16:06,860
who were mentioned in the edict

306
00:16:07,540 --> 00:16:08,540
keep me on my toes.

307
00:16:09,380 --> 00:16:11,260
Now Lu Hongzhu boasts
the greatest power in Qiyuan,

308
00:16:11,740 --> 00:16:12,700
and he increased more people

309
00:16:12,700 --> 00:16:14,140
to find the magic power stone

310
00:16:14,140 --> 00:16:15,180
and the magic girl at the same time.

311
00:16:16,180 --> 00:16:18,420
So I'm afraid he's up to something.

312
00:16:18,620 --> 00:16:20,380
The usurper's ambition must be guarded.

313
00:16:20,540 --> 00:16:22,060
I don't want this throne,

314
00:16:22,500 --> 00:16:25,020
but if he's conspiring to do something
to Qiyuan continent

315
00:16:25,140 --> 00:16:26,060
and No Magic Valley,

316
00:16:26,740 --> 00:16:27,780
I'd definitely stop him.

317
00:16:30,420 --> 00:16:30,980
Well,

318
00:16:31,620 --> 00:16:33,620
why did you let me know it?

319
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:35,820
Lu Hongzhu has sent many people

320
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:37,620
to find the magic girl and the magic power tone,

321
00:16:38,620 --> 00:16:39,660
but I clearly know that

322
00:16:40,140 --> 00:16:42,180
he's not doing it for the Crown Prince.

323
00:16:42,620 --> 00:16:44,570
If he gets the magic power stone,

324
00:16:45,020 --> 00:16:45,820
we may have great trouble.

325
00:16:49,340 --> 00:16:50,180
To tell you the truth,

326
00:16:50,860 --> 00:16:53,700
I have no trace of the magic power stone.

327
00:16:56,580 --> 00:16:57,420
Then what about the magic girl?

328
00:17:00,579 --> 00:17:01,099
Father,

329
00:17:02,220 --> 00:17:03,420
I've been good friends
with Nangong for many years.

330
00:17:03,740 --> 00:17:05,660
You can trust him.

331
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:12,180
As far as I know,

332
00:17:12,930 --> 00:17:15,140
the magic girl died 20 years ago.

333
00:17:15,980 --> 00:17:16,660
Died?

334
00:17:17,329 --> 00:17:18,180
What did you say?

335
00:17:18,810 --> 00:17:19,740
She was dead?

336
00:17:23,150 --> 00:17:31,130
[Hande Dwelling]

337
00:17:24,140 --> 00:17:26,170
Look! Mine was so close.

338
00:17:27,820 --> 00:17:29,620
Alright. I don't want to continue.

339
00:17:29,620 --> 00:17:30,420
Here you are.

340
00:17:38,700 --> 00:17:39,660
You are...

341
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:42,380
My name is Lu Qingqing.

342
00:17:51,500 --> 00:17:53,180
Father? Father!

343
00:17:54,540 --> 00:17:55,860
Qingqing is saying hello to you.

344
00:17:58,660 --> 00:17:59,370
Sorry, young girl.

345
00:18:00,060 --> 00:18:02,020
You remind me of my old friend.

346
00:18:03,570 --> 00:18:04,200
Father,

347
00:18:04,620 --> 00:18:05,890
she is the second daughter of General Lu

348
00:18:05,890 --> 00:18:07,340
on Qiyuan continent, Lu Qingqing.

349
00:18:10,180 --> 00:18:11,300
Are you the daughter of Lu Hongzhu?

350
00:18:11,860 --> 00:18:13,220
Do you know my father?

351
00:18:14,340 --> 00:18:15,780
I only met him once.

352
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:16,900
Great Commander,

353
00:18:17,540 --> 00:18:18,860
I have bothered you a lot today.

354
00:18:19,120 --> 00:18:21,100
Thank you so much for being honest,

355
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:22,480
See you around.

356
00:18:29,740 --> 00:18:30,100
Father,

357
00:18:30,340 --> 00:18:30,780
I'll go with them.

358
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:37,980
The bazaar in No Magic Valley is so bustling!

359
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:38,860
So interesting!

360
00:18:38,900 --> 00:18:39,980
We're here to buy things,

361
00:18:40,060 --> 00:18:40,760
rather than play.

362
00:18:41,140 --> 00:18:41,940
Buy things?

363
00:18:42,300 --> 00:18:43,460
It's not my birthday yet.

364
00:18:43,460 --> 00:18:44,180
What should we buy?

365
00:18:44,860 --> 00:18:46,180
It's got nothing to do with you!

366
00:18:46,300 --> 00:18:47,220
Don't flatter yourself.

367
00:18:49,940 --> 00:18:51,220
This mask looks good.
It must be suitable for you.

368
00:18:51,580 --> 00:18:52,220
Have a try.

369
00:18:52,860 --> 00:18:54,580
I think this is suitable for you.

370
00:18:54,580 --> 00:18:55,420
You can have a try.

371
00:18:56,780 --> 00:18:57,460
Wait a minute.

372
00:18:58,410 --> 00:19:01,060
Why do I feel that I'm an outsider

373
00:19:01,060 --> 00:19:01,900
next to you two?

374
00:19:16,340 --> 00:19:17,530
Come and catch me!

375
00:19:19,780 --> 00:19:20,820
Try harder!

376
00:19:20,710 --> 00:19:25,700
[Ciyou Kindergarten]

377
00:19:36,220 --> 00:19:37,380
Brother Nangong!

378
00:19:38,580 --> 00:19:39,020
Xiaoyi.

379
00:19:39,020 --> 00:19:40,100
Brother Sikong!

380
00:19:40,650 --> 00:19:41,660
Brother Sikong!

381
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:43,100
Brother Nangong!

382
00:19:44,260 --> 00:19:44,780
Xiaoyi.

383
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:49,020
Xiaoyi. What are you eating?

384
00:19:49,220 --> 00:19:49,660
Grapes!

385
00:19:49,660 --> 00:19:50,380
Grapes, I see.

386
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:51,360
Have you been a good boy lately?

387
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:52,020
Yes!

388
00:19:52,260 --> 00:19:53,140
Brother Nangong,

389
00:19:53,500 --> 00:19:55,220
didn't you tell me that you'd buy me new toys

390
00:19:55,220 --> 00:19:57,020
