391
00:19:57,020 --> 00:19:58,930
Did I keep my promise?

392
00:20:00,020 --> 00:20:01,580
You always keep your promise!

393
00:20:01,580 --> 00:20:02,620
You are a good boy, Xiaoyi.

394
00:20:04,380 --> 00:20:05,650
You are so conscienceless!

395
00:20:06,490 --> 00:20:08,380
You forgot me quickly after seeing
your Brother Nangong!

396
00:20:08,620 --> 00:20:09,900
Hello, Uncle Sikong.

397
00:20:11,970 --> 00:20:13,100
You call him brother,

398
00:20:13,780 --> 00:20:14,660
and call me uncle?

399
00:20:17,660 --> 00:20:18,660
My name is Lu Qingqing.

400
00:20:18,940 --> 00:20:20,360
You can call me Sister Qingqing.

401
00:20:20,660 --> 00:20:21,820
These are the presents for you.

402
00:20:21,900 --> 00:20:22,380
Come on!

403
00:20:22,460 --> 00:20:23,930
-Go. Just go. -Come on.

404
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:24,620
Go.

405
00:20:24,620 --> 00:20:26,220
