406
00:20:26,220 --> 00:20:26,860
Come here.

407
00:20:26,940 --> 00:20:27,780
This is also for you.

408
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:28,820
I want this.

409
00:20:29,340 --> 00:20:29,810
Take it.

410
00:20:29,810 --> 00:20:30,500
Take this. Take it.

411
00:20:31,820 --> 00:20:32,220
Here you are.

412
00:20:32,220 --> 00:20:32,820
Everyone has presents.

413
00:20:32,940 --> 00:20:33,700
These are all yours.

414
00:20:33,820 --> 00:20:34,580
Come on, this is for you.

415
00:20:35,060 --> 00:20:35,660
-Go. -Take this.

416
00:20:36,260 --> 00:20:37,140
Thank you, sister.

417
00:20:37,800 --> 00:20:38,540
Take it.

418
00:20:39,460 --> 00:20:39,980
Xiaoyi,

419
00:20:40,140 --> 00:20:41,020
this is for you.

420
00:20:41,740 --> 00:20:42,580
What should you say?

421
00:20:42,900 --> 00:20:43,980
Thank you, sister.

422
00:20:47,690 --> 00:20:48,300
Sister,

423
00:20:48,660 --> 00:20:51,380
are you Brother Nangong's beloved one?

424
00:20:54,060 --> 00:20:55,020
Kids know nothing.

425
00:20:55,020 --> 00:20:55,820
He is talking nonsense.

426
00:21:01,060 --> 00:21:01,620
Xiaoyi,

427
00:21:02,020 --> 00:21:03,260
tell me bravely,

428
00:21:03,900 --> 00:21:04,690
why did

429
00:21:05,580 --> 00:21:06,370
you guess so?

430
00:21:07,260 --> 00:21:08,380
This is the first time

431
00:21:08,380 --> 00:21:09,900
Brother Nangong brought a sister here,

432
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:12,380
so she must be very special.

433
00:21:15,410 --> 00:21:15,980
Xiaoyi,

434
00:21:16,100 --> 00:21:17,420
let sister play cuju with you, okay?

435
00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:18,300
Go.

436
00:21:19,740 --> 00:21:20,220
Quickly.

437
00:21:21,620 --> 00:21:23,140
Sister, let's play cuju.

438
00:21:23,860 --> 00:21:24,540
Okay.

439
00:21:30,340 --> 00:21:31,020
Special.

440
00:21:32,100 --> 00:21:32,780
Special.

441
00:21:33,540 --> 00:21:34,180
Special.

442
00:21:34,530 --> 00:21:35,540
She is indeed special.

443
00:21:51,540 --> 00:21:52,500
Take it.

444
00:21:59,130 --> 00:21:59,940
Great.

445
00:22:04,060 --> 00:22:04,620
Wan Qing!

446
00:22:13,100 --> 00:22:13,660
Wan Qing.

447
00:22:17,940 --> 00:22:18,650
Miss Wan Qing.

448
00:22:19,540 --> 00:22:20,740
You brought all the toys

449
00:22:20,740 --> 00:22:21,300
the kids asked for.

450
00:22:21,740 --> 00:22:22,940
You really keep your words.

451
00:22:23,340 --> 00:22:24,260
I'll realize everything

452
00:22:24,420 --> 00:22:25,220
I promise to the kids.

453
00:22:26,620 --> 00:22:27,340
By the way, Miss Wan Qing,

454
00:22:27,700 --> 00:22:29,460
the kindergarten was just built,

455
00:22:29,810 --> 00:22:30,650
and you're also new here.

456
00:22:30,900 --> 00:22:32,660
Many facilities and supplies are not enough.

457
00:22:32,660 --> 00:22:33,900
So if there is anything you don't adapt to?

458
00:22:34,740 --> 00:22:35,980
Not at all.

459
00:22:36,540 --> 00:22:37,660
I feel happy to

460
00:22:37,900 --> 00:22:38,660
live with the children.

461
00:22:39,420 --> 00:22:41,020
Well. Then thank you for your hard work.

462
00:22:41,180 --> 00:22:42,180
Just tell me if you are homesick.

463
00:22:42,180 --> 00:22:42,900
I'll give you a few days off.

464
00:22:43,650 --> 00:22:44,260
Don't bother.

465
00:22:44,580 --> 00:22:46,140
Home is meaningless to me.

466
00:22:46,170 --> 00:22:47,100
I'm used to being alone.

467
00:22:47,660 --> 00:22:48,260
Wan Qing,

468
00:22:48,900 --> 00:22:50,100
you won't be alone here.

469
00:22:50,410 --> 00:22:51,250
You also have me...

470
00:22:55,060 --> 00:22:55,620
You have us!

471
00:22:56,620 --> 00:22:57,130
Well,

472
00:22:57,220 --> 00:22:58,020
let me take it for you.

473
00:22:58,380 --> 00:22:59,140
It's too heavy.

474
00:23:01,820 --> 00:23:02,420
Nangong,

475
00:23:02,540 --> 00:23:04,180
you donated money to build Ciyou kindergarten

476
00:23:04,300 --> 00:23:05,660
and visit the kids from time to time.

477
00:23:06,170 --> 00:23:07,340
You have put a lot of effort into it.

478
00:23:07,540 --> 00:23:08,380
Don't mention it.

479
00:23:08,860 --> 00:23:09,290
Look,

480
00:23:09,290 --> 00:23:10,820
so many kids without their parents

481
00:23:10,820 --> 00:23:12,420
can have a family in my kindergarten.

482
00:23:12,580 --> 00:23:13,420
I feel happy, too.

483
00:23:14,180 --> 00:23:15,020
Play by yourself for a while.

484
00:23:16,850 --> 00:23:18,900
So it's you who built this Ciyou Kindergarten.

485
00:23:19,860 --> 00:23:20,580
Can't imagine that, right?

486
00:23:21,140 --> 00:23:22,380
Nangong has made great efforts

487
00:23:22,380 --> 00:23:23,220
to build this kindergarten.

488
00:23:23,860 --> 00:23:24,940
He is like both a father and a mother.

489
00:23:26,580 --> 00:23:27,340
He doesn't say it,

490
00:23:27,700 --> 00:23:28,940
but we all know he is kind-hearted.

491
00:23:29,780 --> 00:23:30,860
This is...

492
00:23:31,940 --> 00:23:32,780
I'm Lu Qingqing,

493
00:23:32,780 --> 00:23:34,290
She is my... my...

494
00:23:34,290 --> 00:23:36,140
My servant girl, Lu Qingqing.

495
00:23:37,020 --> 00:23:38,820
You never go out with a servant.

496
00:23:39,260 --> 00:23:41,380
Why did you take a servant girl today?

497
00:23:42,060 --> 00:23:42,730
Wan Qing,

498
00:23:43,220 --> 00:23:44,020
this servant girl...

499
00:23:45,010 --> 00:23:46,380
She is not an ordinary servant.

500
00:23:46,930 --> 00:23:48,420
I'm from Qiyuan continent.

501
00:23:48,420 --> 00:23:49,540
You can just call me Qingqing.

502
00:23:49,940 --> 00:23:51,380
Qiyuan continent?

503
00:23:52,610 --> 00:23:54,250
It's your first time
to come to No Magic Valley, right?

504
00:23:54,540 --> 00:23:55,130
Yes.

505
00:23:55,260 --> 00:23:56,020
How did you know?

506
00:23:56,620 --> 00:23:58,140
I can tell by your costume.

507
00:23:58,980 --> 00:24:00,060
But forgive me for saying it straight.

508
00:24:00,500 --> 00:24:01,700
Your clothes may not be suitable

509
00:24:02,020 --> 00:24:03,340
for No Magic Valley.

510
00:24:03,740 --> 00:24:05,810
This place is full of thorns and storms.

511
00:24:06,260 --> 00:24:07,740
Your shoes could be torn,

512
00:24:08,060 --> 00:24:09,260
and your clothes could also be scratched.

513
00:24:10,300 --> 00:24:11,420
Then I'll have a change.

514
00:24:21,020 --> 00:24:21,620
This.

515
00:24:24,060 --> 00:24:24,660
OK.

516
00:24:28,540 --> 00:24:30,460
You are truly a girl from Qiyuan continent.

517
00:24:31,460 --> 00:24:33,580
You don't even mind tearing up your clothes.

518
00:24:34,100 --> 00:24:35,500
unlike us in No Magic Valley,

519
00:24:35,940 --> 00:24:37,980
who might wear each clothes
for at least two or three years.

520
00:24:38,980 --> 00:24:40,660
I have many other clothes at home.

521
00:24:41,020 --> 00:24:42,100
I'll send them to you next time,

522
00:24:42,100 --> 00:24:42,940
Miss Wan Qing.

523
00:24:44,020 --> 00:24:44,740
Don't bother.

524
00:24:44,980 --> 00:24:46,100
I'm not used to clothes

525
00:24:46,460 --> 00:24:47,260
from Qiyuan continent.

526
00:24:50,060 --> 00:24:51,700
Well, since we're here,

527
00:24:52,020 --> 00:24:53,980
maybe we can have dinner here tonight.

528
00:24:54,340 --> 00:24:55,100
Right, Nangong?

529
00:24:55,540 --> 00:24:56,260
Yes...

530
00:24:56,650 --> 00:24:58,420
Then we'll trouble you, Miss Wan Qing.

531
00:24:58,860 --> 00:24:59,420
Wan Qing,

532
00:25:00,100 --> 00:25:02,780
you are busy with the business
of the kindergarten recently.

533
00:25:03,420 --> 00:25:04,100
You must be tired.

534
00:25:04,420 --> 00:25:05,620
Remember to take good care of yourself.

535
00:25:06,020 --> 00:25:06,940
You are so skinny now.

536
00:25:07,020 --> 00:25:09,090
So you've done these things

537
00:25:09,860 --> 00:25:11,620
all by yourself.

538
00:25:11,940 --> 00:25:13,060
You are awesome!

539
00:25:13,180 --> 00:25:14,060
Of course.

540
00:25:14,300 --> 00:25:15,060
Wan Qing is in charge of

541
00:25:15,060 --> 00:25:16,610
all the business of Ciyou Kindergarten.

542
00:25:17,100 --> 00:25:18,740
She not only handles it in order,

543
00:25:19,060 --> 00:25:19,340
but also...

544
00:25:19,340 --> 00:25:20,420
What do you want for dinner?

545
00:25:24,580 --> 00:25:25,420
As you like.

546
00:25:25,740 --> 00:25:26,740
Anything you cook tastes good.

547
00:25:27,420 --> 00:25:28,340
Brother Nanggong,

548
00:25:28,420 --> 00:25:29,740
let's go play cuju.

549
00:25:30,100 --> 00:25:30,460
Come on,

550
00:25:30,580 --> 00:25:32,370
let's play cuju!

551
00:25:35,700 --> 00:25:36,300
Wan Qing,

552
00:25:37,540 --> 00:25:38,660
are you free tomorrow?

553
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:39,730
I want...

554
00:25:40,100 --> 00:25:42,140
Tomorrow we'll have a birthday party
for Xiaoyi at the kindergarten.

555
00:25:43,260 --> 00:25:44,500
Miss Wan Qing, let me help you.

556
00:25:46,660 --> 00:25:48,260
How can you do so many things here by yourself

557
00:25:48,540 --> 00:25:49,980
without any magic power?

558
00:25:50,260 --> 00:25:51,420
Can you teach me later?

559
00:25:54,140 --> 00:25:55,300
Take on your shoes first.

560
00:25:55,380 --> 00:25:56,820
I'll fetch a pair for you in the room.

561
00:25:56,820 --> 00:25:57,340
OK.

562
00:26:20,820 --> 00:26:21,540
Miss Wan Qing,

563
00:26:21,780 --> 00:26:23,220
