564
00:26:23,540 --> 00:26:24,980
They all look delicious.

565
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:29,660
It doesn't seem too hard.

566
00:26:29,980 --> 00:26:31,050
You can assign me some work

567
00:26:31,050 --> 00:26:31,780
and I'll help you.

568
00:26:32,730 --> 00:26:33,420
No, thanks.

569
00:26:47,260 --> 00:26:48,820
Even though I've never done it before,

570
00:26:49,100 --> 00:26:50,420
I'm smart enough to learn!

571
00:27:04,580 --> 00:27:05,180
Wan Qing,

572
00:27:08,580 --> 00:27:09,860
I picked these flowers specially for you.

573
00:27:10,490 --> 00:27:11,260
Do you like them?

574
